about.summary: Implements modeling and computational tools for conditional random fields (CRF) model as well as other probabilistic undirected graphical models of discrete data with pairwise and unary potentials.

name: r-crf
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.4-3" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-crf
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/CRF_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/CRF/CRF_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6e476f83a026ee28403f82eb85c26515c65c6ede24aeafc3d7e78be65c608c4a

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}      # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-matrix
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-matrix

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('CRF')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('CRF')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/wulingyun/CRF
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Implements modeling and computational tools for conditional random fields (CRF) model
    as well as other probabilistic undirected graphical models of discrete data with
    pairwise and unary potentials.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - Chris-Lowe-Integrity
